::Rex::

Rex shruggs at Battera's story. "Typical Predacon behavior. You have nothing 
to be ashamed off."

He blinks, realizing that she had been nice to him before, and he should 
probably return the favor. It had been a long time since he had been 
intentionally nice.

"I'm sorry about your friends though. But a few Preds down is never bad," he 
says, the last sentence coming out before he knew what he was saying.
